{
  "stem": "26111.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I guess I must have fainted for, for a little while.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the next, next thing I remember was that, that some boys-- they, they were not Jewish boys-- some of my fellow students and, and torturers were carrying me up, up the stairs of the building, of the school building.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And at the top there was a-- there was a-- there was a teacher standing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he-- he was quite kind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because they were saying to their-- to the-- I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Not the two that were carrying me up, but others were saying, oh, you've got the Jew there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's good.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You beat him unconscious, now-- that kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they didn't know what to say.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They couldn't say, no, no, we're just-- we're helping him because that would give them bad standing [LAUGHS] with their-- with their Nazi comrades.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so all the teachers saw was that I was unconscious.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was being helped by two boys.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And, and he was, under the circumstances, he thought maybe I had been knocked unconscious and that would have been going too far at that time.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That was still going too far.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so that was, I would say, the only time during school, during, during classes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was a lot of anti-Semitic matter inserted into the lessons, especially for history, geography, literature, in which-- the, the, the usual way, what you would expect.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "If you're talking music, Felix Mendelssohn was mentioned as an inferior imitator of the great German composers, the usual kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But I imagine that in Russia it would be mentioned as-- [LAUGHS] they would be mentioned as, as imitators of the great Russian composers.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
